high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter that is left of the microwave.
Pick up the plate from the upper cabinet.
Turn right, move to the microwave.
Put the plate in the microwave, cook it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the counter that is right of the microwave.
Put the plate in the upper cabinet that is right of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved plate into the upper cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left, head past the stove, turn right to face the cabinet above the counter.
Take the plate out of the cabinet above the counter.
Bring the plate to the microwave above the stove, to the right.
Heat the plate in the microwave.
Bring the heated plate to the cabinet right of the microwave.
Put the heated plate in the cabinet right of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated plate in the cabinet right of the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the counter to the left of the oven. Look up at the cabinets.
Open the cabinet and grab the plate inside
Turn right and stop at the microwave
Heat the plate in the microwave and then take it out
Move slightly to the right and look up at the cabinet
Put the plate in the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Moving the plate to a cabinet
